    "Similar sensitivity has been documented on logical reasoning tasks (Lewis and Mitchell, 2024).",
    "Their behavior can be substantially influenced by appending an adversarial string to an existing question (Zou et al., 2023).",
    "The same GPT-4 model that demonstrates impressive spatial awareness in describing how to carefully stack a book, a laptop, nine eggs, a bottle and a nail does very poorly for stacking a pudding, a marshmallow, a toothpick and a glass of water (Mitchell, 2023).",
    "Despite their many amazing feats and human-like interface, LLMs do not reason the way humans reason.",
    "An LLM trained on \"A is B\" will not know \"B is A.\""
